FileName

public FileName(String filename,

         throws CsvBangException

Manage file name. Can insert the file number or date.

List of pattern

  • %n : the number file
  • %d : date format

Parameters:
filename - pattern of file name
datePattern - date pattern (required if you want the date in file name). Use a SimpleDateFormat
Throws:
CsvBangException - if no date pattern is defined or if no File name
